<body>
	
<header>
	When asked about your studies or work, you will need to use certain tenses to describe your activities. Match the tenses a candidate should use to the situations. 
</header>
	
<section id="noscroll">
  <span id="a7" draggable="true">past continuous</span>
  <span id="a8" draggable="true">present continuous</span>
  <span id="a9" draggable="true">present perfect continuous</span>
  <span id="a12" draggable="true">present simple</span>
  <span id="a6" draggable="true">past simple</span>
  <span id="a11" draggable="true">future (with 'will' or 'going to')</span>
  <span id="a10" draggable="true">present perfect</span>
</section>

<section id="body">
  <img class="rightFloat" src="../media/EN_SP_003.jpg" mode="1" id="1001"/>
  <p align="left">1<font face="verdana" size="13">. 3 years ago - Finish school</font>	<input id="q1" type="droptarget"/></p>
  <p align="left">2. Over the last year - Prepare for final exams	<input id="q2" type="droptarget"/></p>
  <p align="left">3. Now - Not yet done exams	<input id="q3" type="droptarget"/></p>
  <p align="left">4. Next year - Do further studies	<input id="q4" type="droptarget"/></p>
  <p align="left">5. Most days - Work hard	<input id="q5" type="droptarget"/></p>
</section>

<section id="fb1">
  <p align="left">1. This is not in the present.</p>
  <p align="left">You don't need to use continuous here.</p>
  <p align="left">The word 'ago' does not refer to the future.</p>
</section>

<section id="fb2">
  <p align="left">2. This is not a habit or something you always do.</p>
  <p align="left">There is a period of time involved that is not over yet.</p>
  <p align="left">The word 'last' is not used for the future.</p>
</section>

<section id="fb3">
  <p align="left">3. This is not something that happened in the past.</p>
  <p align="left">And it is not happening now.</p>
  <p align="left">'Yet' means 'until now', so we are not talking about the future.</p>
</section>

<section id="fb4">
  <p align="left">4. 'Next year' is not in the past or the present.</p>
</section>

<section id="fb5">
  <p align="left">5. This is a habit, not a current action.</p>
  <p align="left">We are interested in now.</p>
</section>

